  08 May 2013; James Rowe <jnrowe@gmail.com> Hammertime-0.2.4.ebuild:
  Use $PYTHON_USEDEP, where possible.

  15 Dec 2012; James Rowe <jnrowe@gmail.com> Hammertime-0.2.4.ebuild:
  Use brace expansion for PYTHON_TARGETS.

  09 Dec 2012; James Rowe <jnrowe@gmail.com> Hammertime-0.2.4.ebuild:
  Use distutils-r1's PYTHON_USEDEPs where possible.

  26 Nov 2012; James Rowe <jnrowe@gmail.com> Hammertime-0.2.4.ebuild:
  Switched to EAPI-5.

  25 Oct 2012; James Rowe <jnrowe@gmail.com> Hammertime-0.2.4.ebuild:
  Updated for distutils-r1 usage.

  31 Jul 2012; James Rowe <jnrowe@gmail.com> Hammertime-0.2.4.ebuild:
  Don't run python-distutils-ng_redoscript, as recent silent updates to
  python-distutils-ng now run it and break packages.

  08 Apr 2012; James Rowe <jnrowe@gmail.com> hammertime-0.2.4.ebuild:
  Switched to python-distutils-ng eclass.

  19 Mar 2012; James Rowe <jnrowe@gmail.com> hammertime-0.2.4.ebuild:
  Switched to EAPI4.

  03 Mar 2012; James Rowe <jnrowe@gmail.com> hammertime-0.2.4.ebuild:
  Removed Python 2.4 support.

  03 Mar 2012; James Rowe <jnrowe@gmail.com> -hammertime-0.1.4.ebuild:
  Removed stale ebuild, newer version will be available for stabilisation
  around the same time.

  01 Feb 2012; James Rowe <jnrowe@gmail.com> hammertime-0.1.4.ebuild:
  Removed old src_prepare, README.md hasn't been included since 0.1.3.

